WEBVTT

00:03:57.835 --> 00:04:00.730
wamuachie mrembo wake na sharti

00:04:00.730 --> 00:04:03.842
asimtazame kamwe mpaka watoke.

00:04:03.842 --> 00:04:05.681
Hivyo anatoka na kutoka na kutoka

00:04:05.681 --> 00:04:09.939
na anashindwa kujizuia. Anamuangalia,
anampoteza milele.

00:04:09.939 --> 00:04:12.773
Na taarifa yote hii huko nje, inaweza kua
wazo zuri

00:04:12.773 --> 00:04:18.521
kutokuangalia mbali sana kwenye ya
kale ya uwapendao.

00:04:18.521 --> 00:04:21.362
Somo namba tatu: Atalanta.

00:04:21.362 --> 00:04:25.811
Mkimbiaji bora. Anashindana na yeyote.

00:04:25.811 --> 00:04:28.221
Kama ukishinda, angekuoa.

00:04:28.221 --> 00:04:31.146
Kama ukishindwa, unakufa.